  "vuln_description": "The vulnerability allows an attacker to gain verified access to GitLab's Slack (or similar services) by abusing the issue creation via email feature. This is possible because the email addresses used for creating issues are valid @gitlab.com addresses, which can be used to bypass verification processes for services like Slack.",
